Step 2: Set App Name and Purpose
App Name: LinkedInScaler
Description:
An AI-powered app to generate LinkedIn posts based on topic, writing style, post category, and preferred content length.
Step 3: Add Input Field – Main Topic
Click Add Input → Text Input
Configure:
Label: Enter Main Topic / Theme
Placeholder: e.g., AI in Marketing, Career Growth, Personal Branding
Required: Yes
Save the field as:
Variable Name: topic
Step 4: Add Dropdown – Writing Style
Click Add Input → Dropdown
Configure:
Label: Select Writing Style
Required: Yes
Add these options:
Professional
Inspirational
Educational
Storytelling
Conversational
Promotional
Save as:
Variable Name: writing_style
Step 5: Add Dropdown – Post Category
Click Add Input → Dropdown
Configure:
Label: Select Post Category
Required: Yes
Add these options:
Thought Leadership
Personal Story
Industry Insight
Case Study
Announcement
How-To / Tips
Career Advice
Save as:
Variable Name: post_category
Step 6: Add Slider – Post Length
Click Add Input → Slider
Configure:
Label: Select Post Length
Required: Yes
Set values:
Min: Short
Mid: Medium
Max: Large
Save as:
Variable Name: post_length
